                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <h3> How to use private nugget in Azure funciton</h3>
                                <p> In order to use a private nugget pacakge you need a nuget.config file. Example is at right side.</p>
                                <p> In this nuget.config. You need to specify you nugget pacakge name and path. If this nugget is built in vsft. You need to give the user name and vsts access token.</p>
                                <p> For whom don't know vsts access token. Please check <a href="https://www.visualstudio.com/en-us/docs/setup-admin/team-services/use-personal-access-tokens-to-authenticate">here</a></p>
                                <p> Please make sure your access token will have the package access scope only.</p>
                                <p> Upload this file to the azure function folder and edit your Project.json.</p>
                            </div>
