                                <h3> How to directly refer dlls in Azure funciton</h3>
                                <p> In order to directly refer dlls in Azure function. You need to upload the dlls in to the app plan and refer using #r.</p>
                                <p> Go back to your function app portal. Find function app settings -> go to Kudu -> using Kudu create a bin folder and copy your dlls into the bin folder.</p>
                                <p> For whom don't know how to use kudus. Please check <a href="https://github.com/projectkudu/kudu/wiki/Kudu-console">here</a></p>
                                <p> In your csx code, make a line like #r "path of your dll". Right side is an example.</p>
                            </div>
